Key Components of AML
â€¢	KYC (Know Your Customer) â€“ Verify user identity
â€¢	Transaction Monitoring â€“ Track suspicious activity
â€¢	Risk Assessment â€“ Identify high-risk users or regions
â€¢	Reporting â€“ File suspicious activity reports (SARs)
â€¢	Compliance Checks â€“ Follow government regulations
________________________________________
AML in Crypto & Blockchain
â€¢	Exchanges must verify users
â€¢	Wallet activity is monitored
â€¢	Large or unusual transfers are flagged
â€¢	Blockchain analytics track fund movement
Even though crypto is decentralized, AML compliance is mandatory for platforms.
